Cp%3EBut%20as%20one%20of%20Musk's%20recent%20livestreams%20demonstrates%2C%20they%20offer%20Tesla%20fans%20and%20those%20interested%20in%20his%20various%20other%20companies%2C%20like%20SpaceX%20or%20Neuralink%2C%20another%20channel%20to%20hear%20the%20billionaire%20riff%20on%20his%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sessions%20last%20several%20hours%20(his%20latest%20stream%20was%20over%20five%20hours%20long)%2C%20and%20while%20Musk%20was%20partly%20focused%20on%20playing%20a%20video%20game%20%E2%80%94%20in%20this%20case%2C%20%26quot%3BDiablo%20IV%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20he%20also%20responded%20to%20people%20in%20the%20livestream%20chat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGaming%20aside%2C%20it's%20classic%20Musk.%20He%20talks%20in%20a%20stream-of-consciousness%20fashion%20about%20Tesla%2C%20SpaceX%2C%20X%2C%20Neuralink%2C%20and%20the%20future%2C%20sometimes%20touching%20on%20some%20of%20his%20go-to%20points%2C%20such%20as%20his%20concerns%20about%20human%20population%20levels%20and%20encouraging%20his%20friends%20to%20have%20more%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20latest%20stream%2C%20for%20example%2C%20he%20talked%20about%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20logistics%20of%20terraforming%20and%20building%20a%20self-sustaining%20city%20on%20Mars%20%E2%80%94%20which%20he%20estimates%20could%20be%20done%20in%2020%20to%2030%20years.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20we'll%20launch%20the%20first%20Starship%20to%20Mars%20in%20less%20than%20three%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20he'd%20like%20to%20die%20on%20Mars%2C%20Musk%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BSure%2C%20why%20not%20die%20on%20Mars.%20I%20just%20don't%20want%20to%20die%20on%20impact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHis%20AI%20company%2C%20xAI%2C%20bringing%20its%20chatbot%20Grok%20to%20Tesla.%20Musk%20said%20users%20will%20be%20able%20to%20ask%20it%20to%20go%20pick%20up%20a%20friend%20or%20groceries.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHis%20optimism%20about%20Optimus%20humanoid%20robots%2C%20which%20he%20anticipates%20will%20