.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20median%20house%20price%20in%20San%20Jose%20last%20year%20was%2011.9%20times%20the%20gross%20median%20household%20income%20in%20that%20market%2C%20per%20the%20report%20published%20by%20the%20Frontier%20Centre%20for%20Public%20Policy%2C%20a%20Canadian%20think%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20median%20price-to-income%20ratio%20was%2010.9%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20and%20not%20much%20lower%20in%20San%20Francisco%20(9.7)%20and%20San%20Diego%20(9.5).%20In%20other%20words%2C%20if%20the%20median%20household%20income%20was%20%24100%2C000%20in%20those%20markets%2C%20the%20median%20home%20cost%20more%20than%20%24900%2C000%20in%20the%20two%20most%20affordable%20locales%2C%20and%20almost%20%241.2%20million%20in%20San%20Jose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20classified%20a%20ratio%20of%209%20or%20higher%20as%20%26quot%3Bimpossibly%20unaffordable%2C%26quot%3B%20saying%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzandi-moodys-house-prices-mortgage-interest-rates-affordability-crisis-market-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evirtually%20unfeasible%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20middle-income%20housing%20to%20raise%20enough%20financing%20to%20afford%20a%20typical%20home%20in%20the%20area.%20That%20level%20of%20unaffordability%20didn't%20exist%20three%20decades%20ago%2C%20they%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20analyzed%20housing%20affordability%20in%2094%20major%20markets%20across%20eight%20countries%20including%20the%20US%2C%20Canada%2C%20Australia%2C%20China%2C%20and%20the%20UK.%20Hong%20Kong%20(16.7)%20topped%20the%20ranking%20for%20a%2013th%20time%2C%20followed%20by%20Sydney%20(13.3)%20and%20Vancouver%20(12.3)%2C%20which%20have%20secured%20top-three%20spots%20in%2015%20and%2016%20of%20the%20last%2016%20years%20respectively.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHonolulu%20(10.5)%2C%20Melbourne%20(9.8)%2C%20Adelaide%20(9.7)%2C%20and%20Toronto%20(9.3)%20rounded%20out%20the%20list%20of%20