ncentration%20camp.%20While%20Glazer%E2%80%99s%20film%20was%20a%20work%20of%20fiction%2C%20based%20on%20Martin%20Amis%E2%80%99%20novel%2C%20Volker%E2%80%99s%20film%20is%20a%20documentary.%20Exploring%20the%20legacy%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Naman%20Ramachandran%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fholocaust-doc-the-commandants-shadow-zone-of-interest-1236040789%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fholocaust-doc-the-commandants-shadow-zone-of-interest-1236040789%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fholocaust-doc-the-commandants-shadow-zone-of-interest-1236040789%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20In%20Numbers%3A%20Brand%20Modi%20Is%20Still%20The%20Key%20Difference%20Between%20BJP%20And%20Others%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F9m078hlg_pm-modi-oath-third-term-ians_625x300_09_June_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202024%20mandate%20has%20reignited%20the%20debate%20around%20'Brand%20Modi'.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party's%20(BJP)%20inability%20to%20cross%20the%20majority%20mark%20on%20its%20own%20has%20led%20some%20analysts%20to%20claim%20the%20brand%20has%20weakened%20considerably.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20despite%20losses%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20still%20emerged%20as%20the%20single-largest%20party.%20This%20coupled%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20equalled%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru's%20record%20of%20winning%20a%20successive%20third%20term%20is%20being%20seen%20by%20many%20as%20proof%20that%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20brand%20is%20still%20intact.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20won%20240%20seats%20in%20the%20recently%20concluded%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20won%2099.%20Alliance-wise%2C%20while%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20won%20292%20seats%20and%20around%2044%25%20votes%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20got%20234%20seats%20and%20registered%20a%2041%25%20vote%20share.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Modi%20premium'%20or%20the%20'Modi%20factor'%20can%20be%20defined%20as%20PM%20Modi's%20ability%20to%20attract%20voters%20who%20are%20not%20among%20the%20party's%20core%20vote%20banks.%20Post-poll%20data%20released%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Developing%20Societies%20(CSDS)%20and%20some%20associated%20research%20carried%20out%20by%20this%20author%20point%20to%20some%20answers%20to%20questions%20about%20the%20popularity%20of%20this%20'brand'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELocalised%20Elections%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20national%20level%2C%20the%20election%20this%20year%20was%20more%20localised%20than%20the%202019%20polls.%20Just%2010%25%20of%20voters%20said%20they%20considered%20the%20prime%20ministerial%20face%20as%20the%20most%20important%20factor%20while%20voting%20-%20%C2%A0down%20from%2017%25%20in%202019.%20Correspondingly%2C%20the%20share%20of%20voters%20who%20focused%20on%20their%20local%20candidates%20increased%20from%2031%25%20in%202019%20to%2036%25%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20Prime%20Ministerial%20preference%2C%20while%20Narendra%20Modi%20received%2041%25%20support%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20ratings%20were%20just%20around%2027%25.%20Though%20the%20gap%20is%20still%20significant%2C%20it%20has%20narrowed%20since%202019%2C%20when%20Modi's%20ratings%20were%2047%25%20and%20Rahul's%2023%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20multiply%20the%20leadership%20gap%20by%20the%20number%20of%20respondents%20voting%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20prime%20ministerial%20face%2C%20it%20can%20be%20said%20that%20in%20terms%20of%20vote%20share%2C%20the%20BJP's%20leadership%20advantage%20fetched%20the%20party%20and%20its%20allies%20roughly%204.1%25%20votes%20in%202019.%20This%20has%20declined%20to%20just%201.4%25%20in%202024.%20Further%2C%20in%20the%20previous%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%2032%25%20of%20voters%20who%20backed%20the%20BJP%20said%20they%20would%20not%20have%20voted%20for%20it%20if%20Modi%20were%20not%20its%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate.%20The%20share%20of%20such%20voters%20has%20declined%20to%2025%25%20now%2C%20veering%20closer%20to%20the%202014%20figure%20of%2027%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStill%20The%20USP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20PM%20Modi's%20popularity%20helps%20not%20just%20the%20BJP%20but%20also%20its%20allies.%20In%202014%2C%20he%20fetched%2020%25%20of%20votes%20for%20the%20BJP's%20allies%2C%2025%25%20in%202019%2C%20and%2027%25%20in%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20in%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20recorded%20a%2037.8%25%20vote%20share.%20According%20to%20this%20author's%20research%2C%2025.7%25%20of%20this%20came%20from%20its%20core%20ideological%20base%2C%20while%2012.1%25%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20the%20'Modi%20factor'.%20This%20year%2C%20of%20the%20BJP's%2036.6%25%20vote%20share%2C%20the%20core%20base%20accounts%20for%20about%2027.4%25%20votes%20and%20the%20'Modi%20factor'%20around%209.2%25.%20This%20implies%20that%20the%20'Modi%20premium'%20has%20declined%20from%20around%2012%25%20in%202019%20to%20around%209%25%20now.%20Nonetheless%2C%20Modi%20still%20fetches%209%25%20support%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20three%20times%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20vote%20shares%20of%20the%20NDA%20and%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20argued%20that%20without%20Modi%2C%20the%20NDA%20would%20have%20struggled%20to%20form%20a%20government.%20He%20was%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20two%20blocs.%20The%20numbers%20below%20illustrate%20this%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%202014%2C%20the%20NDA%20bagged%20around%205.5%20crore%20votes%20based%20on%20the%20Modi%20factor.%20The%20NDA's%20lead%20over%20the%20Congress-led%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20was%20around%208.7%20crore%20votes.%20This%20means%20the%20Modi%20factor%20accounted%20for%2063%25%20of%20NDA's%20lead.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20next%20elections%2C%20the%20NDA%20got%20around%208.5%20crore%20votes%2C%20while%20the%20NDA's%20lead%20was%2011%20crore.%20Thus%2C%20the%20Modi%20factor%20accounted%20for%2077%25%20of%20NDA's%20winning%20margin.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20latest%20round%2C%20Modi%20fetched%20the%20NDA%20around%207.1%20crore%20votes%2C%20while%20the%20NDA's%20lead%20over%20India%20was%20around%202%20crore.%20The%20Modi%20factor%20thus%20accounted%20for%20much%20more%20than%20the%20NDA's%20lead%20and%20was%20the%20key%20differentiating%20factor%20between%20it%20and%20the%20opposition%20front.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20the%20BJP's%20victory%20in%20240%20seats%20and%20the%20NDA's%20in%20292%20seats%20may%20have%20been%20difficult%20without%20Modi.%20Brand%20Modi%20may%20have%20aged%20-%20or%20perhaps%20peaked%20as%20well%20-%20after%2010%20years%20in%20power%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20the%20prime%20differentiator%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718700300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F9m078hlg_pm-modi-oath-third-term-ians_625x300_09_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbrand-modi-is-still-the-key-difference-between-bjp-and-others-5914932%22%2C%22summary%22%