%26quot%3B%20overlooking%20a%20beach%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20excursion%20left%20everyone%20stunned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CRZ%20(Coastal%20Regulatory%20Zone)%20clearance%20was%20given%20by%20the%20central%20government%20in%20May%202021%20for%20a%20tourism%20project%20to%20be%20developed%20on%20Rushikonda%20Hills%20by%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Tourism%20Development%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETDP's%20national%20general%20secretary%20Nara%20Lokesh%2C%20however%2C%20says%20Jagan%20Reddy%20decided%20to%20use%20it%20exclusively%20as%20his%20camp%20office%20and%20built%20it%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%20500%20crore%20from%20the%20state%20exchequer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rushikonda%20palace%20is%20spread%20over%20a%209.88-acre%20sea-facing%20site.%20Ganta%20Srinivas%20Rao%20said%20the%20previous%20government%20had%20built%20it%20in%20secrecy%2C%20using%20public%20funds%20on%20luxurious%20amenities%2C%20high-quality%20furnishing%2C%20sparkling%20chandeliers%2C%20bathtubs%20and%20the%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Flqf20ko8_palace-1_625x300_18_June_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rao%20compared%20the%20extravagance%20to%20palaces%20built%20by%20Iraq%20dictator%20Saddam%20Hussein%20and%2C%20closer%20home%2C%20Gali%20Janardhan%20Reddy.%20The%20%26quot%3Bpalace%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20argued%2C%20includes%20a%20large%20conference%20hall%20designed%20for%20reviews%20and%20meetings%20-%20not%20exactly%20a%20feature%20of%20tourist%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20construction%20costs%20were%20kept%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20confidential%26quot%3B%20and%20contracts%20were%20awarded%20to%20supporters%20of%20Jagan's%20YSRCP%2C%20the%20TDP%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TDP%20leader%20said%20green%20resorts%20for%20tourism%20on%20Rushikonda%2C%20which%20generated%20an%20annual%20income%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%208%20crore%2C%20were%20demolished%20for%20the%20palace.%20The%20state%20government%20misled%20the%20courts%2C%20he%20alleged.%20Initially%2C%20the%20state%20government%20called%20it%20a%20star%20hotel%2C%20then%20a%20%26quot%3BCM%20camp%20office%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20later%20a%20tourism%20project%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20was%20launched%20as%20a%20star%20hotel%20with%20a%20budget%20of%20Rs%2091%20crore%2C%20with%20a%2015-month%20deadline.%20However%2C%20Rs%2095%20crore%20was%20spent%20just%20on%20leveling%20the%20land%2C%20and%20another%20Rs%2021%20crore%20to%20beautify%20the%20surroundings%2C%20the%20TDP%20alleges.%20To%20keep%20the%20construction%20activities%20hidden%2C%2020-foot%20barricades%20were%20erected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fhph4q4n_palace_625x300_18_June_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mr%20Rao%2C%20when%20the%20project%20was%20challenged%2C%20a%20High%20Court%20expert%20committee%20found%20several%20violations%20but%20construction%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%2C%20not%20even%20new%20Chief%20Minister%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20and%20his%20deputy%20Pawan%20Kalyan%2C%20really%20knew%20what%20was%20coming%20up%20behind%20the%20barricades.%20%26quot%3BDivine%20intervention%20prevented%20Jagan%20from%20using%20the%20palace%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rao%20quipped%2C%20referring%20to%20Jagan's%20election%20rout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Feic98c5g_palace_625x300_18_June_24.jpg%5C%22