indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Franbir-kapoors-animal-co-star-saurabh-sachdeva-gives-a-major-update-on-animal-park-see-inside%2Farticleshow%2F111079354.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSeparate%20Teams%20For...%26quot%3B%3A%20Gambhir's%20'Demands'%20For%20Becoming%20Coach%20-%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20cricketer%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20is%20set%20to%20appear%20for%20an%20interview%20for%20the%20men's%20cricket%20team%20head%20coach%20position%20in%20Mumbai%20with%20BCCI%20secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20and%20other%20officials%2C%20say%20sources.%20%26quot%3BGauti%20(Gautam%20Gambhir)%20will%20be%20travelling%20today%20to%20Mumbai%20around%2012%20pm%20for%20the%20interview%20at%20BCCI%20Headquarters.%20It%20is%20almost%20confirmed%20that%20he%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20next%20head%20coach%20as%20the%20BCCI%20has%20agreed%20to%20the%20terms%20he%20presented%20for%20the%20head%20coach.%20The%20new%20head%20coach%20of%20the%20men's%20cricket%20team%20will%20soon%20be%20revealed.%20The%20meeting%20is%20scheduled%20between%202-4%20pm%2C%E2%80%9D%20source%20privy%20to%20BCCI%20told%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGambhir%20put%20up%20a%20few%20demands%20in%20front%20of%20the%20BCCI%20for%20the%20head%20coach%20position%20such%20as%20full%20command%20on%20the%20team%2C%20separate%20teams%20for%20white-ball%20and%20red-ball%2C%20which%20IANS%20understands%20that%20the%20BCCI%20has%20already%20accepted%20and%20is%20keen%20to%20appoint%20him%20for%20the%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%20officially%20invited%20applications%20for%20the%20India%20head%20coach's%20post%20with%20May%2027%20set%20as%20the%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20job%20description%2C%20the%20new%20India%20men's%20head%20coach%20would%20be%20for%20all%20three%20formats%20from%20July%202024%20till%20December%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDravid's%20original%20contract%20as%20India's%20head%20coach%20began%20after%20the%202021%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20November%20and%20had%20come%20to%20an%20end%20with%20the%202023%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20at%20home%20and%20was%20extended%20till%20this%20year's%20T20I%20spectacle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20recent%20event%2C%20Gambhir%20suggested%20that%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20bigger%20honour%20than%20coaching%20the%20national%20team%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20love%20to%20coach%20the%20Indian%20team.%20There%20is%20no%20bigger%20honour%20than%20coaching%20your%20national%20team.%20You%20are%20representing%20140%20crore%20Indians%20and%20those%20across%20the%20globe%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2042-year-old%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGambhir%20was%20part%20of%20India's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20winning%20team%20in%202007%20and%20the%202011%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718696400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Ffgsb39ug_gautam-gambhir-bcci_625x300_06_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhirs-interview-for-india-coach-inside-details-terms-he-presented-to-bcci-5914351%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20per%20the%20job%20description%2C%20the%20new%20India%20men's%20head%20coach%20would%20be%20for%20all%20three%20formats%20from%20July%202024%20till%20December%202027.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhirs-interview-for-india-coach-inside-details-terms-he-presented-to-bcci-5914351%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhirs-interview-for-india-coach-inside-details-terms-he-presented-to-bcci-5914351%2Famp%2F1