id.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20-%20while%20hearing%20a%20batch%20of%20petitions%20over%20the%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20exam%20-%20said%20it%20expects%20a%20%26quot%3Btimely%20action%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20NTA%20and%20that%20the%20agency%20must%20ensure%20that%20all%20candidates%20are%20treated%20fairly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20an%20agency%20which%20is%20conducting%20the%20examination%2C%20you%20must%20act%20fair.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20mistake%2C%20say%20yes%2C%20this%20is%20a%20mistake%2C%20and%20this%20is%20the%20action%20we%20are%20going%20to%20take.%20At%20least%20that%20inspires%20confidence%20in%20your%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0a%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Vikram%20Nath%20and%20Justice%20SVN%20Bhatti%20told%20the%20NTA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20observed%20that%20the%20agency%20shouldn't%20forget%20the%20efforts%20students%20put%20in%20to%20prepare%20for%20one%20of%20the%20toughest%20entrance%20exams%20in%20the%20country%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImagine%20a%20person%20who%20has%20played%20fraud%20on%20the%20system%20becomes%20a%20doctor%2C%20he%20is%20more%20deleterious%20to%20the%20society.%20Children%20study%20hard%20to%20get%20through%20NEET%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20next%20hearing%20in%20the%20case%20will%20be%20held%20on%20July%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20NTA%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20grace%20marks%20given%20to%201%2C563%20candidates%20in%20the%20NEET-UG%20exam%20would%20be%20scrapped%20and%20the%20candidates%20had%20the%20option%20of%20taking%20the%20exam%20again%20on%20June%2023.%20The%20results%20of%20the%20re-test%20will%20be%20declared%20before%20June%2030%2C%20the%20top%20court%20was%20told.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20any%20of%20these%20candidates%20chose%20to%20not%20take%20the%20re-test%2C%20their%20earlier%20score%20would%20be%20reinstated%20without%20the%20extra%20marks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResults%20for%20the%20medical%20entrance%20examination%2C%20which%20was%20taken%20by%2024%20lakh%20students%20on%20May%205%2C%20were%20declared%20on%20June%204.%20Allegations%20of%20an%20exam%20paper%20leak%20soon%20surfaced.%20As%20many%20as%2067%20students%20got%20a%20perfect%20score%20of%20720%2F720.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrace%20marks%20were%20given%20to%20several%20students%20allegedly%20to%20compensate%20for%20loss%20of%20time%20at%20the%20exam%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20student%20organisations%20have%20protested%20over%20the%20alleged%20NEET%20irregularities%2C%20including%20wrong%20question%20papers%20being%20distributed%2C%20Optical%20Mark%20Recognition%20(OMR)%20sheets%20being%20torn%2C%20or%20delays%20in%20the%20distribution%20of%20the%20sheets.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718695560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fqho8m9m_neet-protest_625x300_16_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-theres-even-0-001-negligence-supreme-court-reprimands-nta-amid-neet-row-5914090%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20concerns%20about%20the%20National%20Eligibility-cum-Entrance%20Test%20(NEET)%20for%20admission%20into%20medical%20colleges%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%2C%20which%20conducts%20the%20nationwide%20exam%20for%20medical%20college%20aspirant%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-theres-even-0-001-negligence-supreme-court-reprimands-nta-amid-neet-row-5914090%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-theres-even-0-001-negligence-supreme-court-reprimands-nta-amid-neet-row-5914090%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-theres-even-0-001-negligence-supreme-court-reprimands-nta-amid-neet-row-5914090%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Plastic%20Surgeon%2C%2041%2C%20Arrested%20After%20Wife%20Dies%20During%20Surgery%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2041-year-old%20plastic%20surgeon%20in%20the%20United%20States%20has%20been%20arrested%20over%20the%20death%20of%20his%20wife%20who%20went%20into%20cardiac%20arrest%20on%20his%20operating%20table%20in%20November%20last%20year.%20The%20doctor%2C%20identified%20as%20Benjamin%20Brown%2C%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20on%20Monday%20and%20charged%20with%20one%20count%20of%20second-degree%20felony%20homicide%20for%20alleged%20manslaughter%20by%20culpable%20negligence%20in%20the%20death%20of%20his%20wife%20Hillary%20Ellington%20Brown.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Independent%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20turned%20himself%20in%20to%20the%20police%20after%20a%20warrant%20was%20put%20out%20for%20his%20arrest%20on%20Friday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20note%2C%20the%20Santa%20Rosa%20County%20Sheriff's%20Office%20said%20deputies%20responded%20to%20the%2041-year-old's%20practice%2C%20Restore%20Plastic%20Surgery%2C%20in%20Florida%2C%20for%20a%20medical%20emergency%20on%20November%2021.%20Upon%20arriving%20at%20the%20scene%2C%20first%20responders%20located%20a%20female%20victim%20-%20later%20identified%20as%20Hillary%20Brown%20-%20suffering%20from%20cardiac%20arrest.%20She%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20hospital%2C%20where%20she%20was%20put%20on%20life%20support%20before%20she%20was%20pronounced%20dead.%20An%20autopsy%20into%20her%20death%20is%20pending.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20autopsy%20protocol%20typically%20takes%20several%20months%20as%20it%20usually%20is%20dependent%20on%20extensive%20laboratory%20and%20toxicology%20tests%20as%20well%20as%20the%20information%20gathered%20by%20our%20Major%20Crimes%20detectives%20concerning%20the%20circumstances%20of%20the%20death%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20department%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Brown%20is%20being%20held%20in%20the%20county's%20jail%20pending%20his%20bond%20hearing%2C%20the%20statement%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fsantarosasheriff%252Fposts%252Fpfbid02jGhtrD1r2Jvs6gbsLENjA4eKKJb76zc8X6EjNvqUiriinNH119X3G66qrMdqcwrNl%26show_text%3Dtrue%26width%3D500%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22250%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Famericas%2Fcrime%2Fdr-benjamin-brown-pensacola-florida-plastic-surgeon-b2564333.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Independent%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20on%20the%20day%20Ms%20Hillary%20went%20into%20cardiac%20arrest%2C%20she%20was%20scheduled%20to%20undergo%20miniature%20muscle%20plication%2Fabdominal%20scar%20revision%2C%20bilateral%20arm%20liposuction%2C%20lip%20injections%2C%20and%20ear%20adjustment%20procedures.%20She%20reportedly%20prepared%20her%20own%20anaesthesia%20before%20the%20surgeries.%20She%20also%20ingested%20a%20handful%20of%20multicoloured%20pills%2C%20including%20Valium.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20before%20the%20procedures%2C%20she%20began%20experiencing%20symptoms%20relating%20to%20sedation.%20When%20she%20went%20into%20the%20operating%20room%2C%20her%20husband%20administered%20additional%20anaesthesia%20without%20being%20able%20to%20verify%20what%20his%20wife%20took.%20He%20subsequently%20did%20not%20record%20his%20wife's%20medication%20and%20dosage.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20his%20wife%20told%20him%20that%20her%20vision%20was%20becoming%20blurry%20and%20she%20saw%20%26quot%3Borange%26quot%3B.%20Moreover%2C%20she%20experienced%20restlessness%2C%20muscle%20twitching%20and%20blurred%20vision%20which%20are%20common%20symptoms%20of%20toxicity.%20The%2041-year-old%2C%20however%2C%20continued%20injecting%20drugs%20into%20her%20face%2C%20following%20which%20she%20became%20unresponsive%20and%20started%20to%20seize.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Findian-astrologer-stands-by-prediction-claims-world-war-3-is-days-away-5913389%5C%22%3EIndian%20Astrologer%20Stands%20By%20Prediction%2C%20Claims%20World%20War%203%20Is%20Days%20Away%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20point%2C%20a%20medical%20assistant%20asked%20the%20doctor%20if%20they%20should%20call%20emergency%20services%20and%20he%20said%20%26quot%3Bno%26quot%3B.%20In%20the%20next%2020%20minutes%2C%20the%20assistant%20asked%20again%20and%20he%20said%20%26quot%3Bno%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bwait%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20outlet%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plastic%20surgeon%20began%20to%20panic%20and%20requested%20his%20assistants%20to%20bring%20him%20supplies%2C%20including%20an%20oxygen%20tank%20and%20stethoscope.%20However%2C%20as%20the%20medical%20assistant%20was%20new%2C%20they%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20find%20the%20items.%20Meanwhile%2C%20instead%20of%20calling%20an%20ambulance%2C%20Brown%20allegedly%20%26quot%3Bshouted%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20staff%2C%20asking%20%26quot%3BWhat%20medication%20did%20she%20take%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%2010%20to%2020%20minutes%20after%20Hillary%20Brown%20suffered%20a%20seizure%2C%20Brown%20instructed%20an%20assistant%20to%20call%20911%2C%20but%20his%20wife%20never%20regained%20consciousness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20medical%20board%20determined%20that%20Brown's%20treatment%20of%20his%20wife%20was%20%26quot%3Bcareless%20and%20haphazard%26quot%3B.%20Moreover%2C%20in%20May%2C%20Florida's%20Department%20of%20Health%20issued%20an%20emergency%20order%20restricting%20the%20doctor's%20medical%20license%20to%20only%20perform%20procedures%20or%20surgeries%20in%20a%20licensed%20hospital%20while%20under%20the%20supervision%20of%20a%20licensed%20physician.%20The%20department%20is%20pursuing%20disciplinary%20action%20in%20the%20case.%20Ben%20Brown%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20chosen%20to%20challenge%20the%20allegations%20made%20against%20him%20and%20the%20case%20will%20be%20heard%20by%20the%20Division%20for%20Administrative%20Hearings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718694900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F7apol1k8_benjamin-brown_625x300_18_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-plastic-surgeon-41-arrested-after-wife-dies-during-surgery-5914477%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2041-year-old%20plastic%20surgeon%20in%20the%20United%20States%20has%20been%20arrested%20over%20the%20death%20of%20his%20wife%20who%20went%20into%20cardiac%20arrest%20on%20his%20operating%20table%20in%20November%20last%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-plastic-surgeon-41-arrested-after-wife-dies-during-surgery-5914477%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-plastic-surgeon-41-arrested-after-wife-dies-during-surgery-5914477%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-plastic-surgeon-41-arrested-after-wife-dies-during-surgery-5914477%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDon't%20Waste%20Time%20In%20Pak%26quot%3B%3A%20Harbhajan's%20'Offer'%20For%20Kirsten%20After%20Outburst%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20early%20T20%20World%20Cup%20exit%20was%20not%20enough%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20cricket%20team%20has%20been%20dealt%20some%20bigger%20blows%20with%20a%20viral%20remark%20by%20its%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gary%20Kirsten%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F260-gary-kirsten-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGary%20Kirsten%3C%2Fa%3E%20going%20viral.%20According%20to%20media%20reports%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20Kirsten%2C%20who%20guided%20India%20to%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20triumph%20i