eel%20%26quot%3Bswept%20off%20their%20feet%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20successful%20romantic%20encounter.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThirty-five%20per%20cent%20believe%20the%20relationship%20is%20doomed%20if%20they%20don't%20feel%20swept%20off%20their%20feet%20on%20a%20first%20date.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EAttractive%20traits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnEighty%20per%20cent%20find%20self-confidence%20attractive.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSeventy-five%20per%20cent%20are%20attracted%20to%20people%20who%20are%20proud%20of%20their%20life%20accomplishments.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSeventy-three%20per%20cent%20like%20people%20who%20go%20above%20and%20beyond%20on%20a%20first%20date.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnForty-two%20per%20cent%20find%20financial%20stability%20and%20cooking%20skills%20to%20be%20the%20most%20attractive%20traits.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHaving%20a%20nice%20home%20(24%25)%2C%20a%20cultured%20taste%20in%20music%20(21%25)%2C%20and%20a%20good%20fashion%20sense%20(20%25)%20are%20also%20highly%20attractive%20qualities.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EViews%20on%20Hypergamy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnForty-five%20per%20cent%20believe%20it%20is%20acceptable%20to%20showcase%20their%20success%20and%20wealth%20on%20a%20first%20date.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThirty-one%20per%20cent%20consider%20financial%20success%20attractive.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThirty-nine%20per%20cent%20believe%20finding%20a%20partner%20who%20exhibits%20hypergamic%20traits%20contributes%20significantly%20to%20personal%20growth.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20hypergamy%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnFrom%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Real%20Housewives%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20%3Cem%3EBridgerton%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20notion%20of%20marrying%20into%20higher%20social%20ranks%20has%20always%20interested%20people.%20This%20trend%2C%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Bhypergamy%2C%26quot%3B%20involves%20families%20climbing%20the%20social%20ladder%20through%20strategic%20marriages%2C%20a%20conce