ble-as-an-app-for-android-phone-users-in-india-124061800286_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Bengal%20Has%20Lessons%20For%20India%20In%20Sending%20More%20Women%20To%20Parliament%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F7ko6i7hc_new-parliament-ani-new-lok-sabha-ani_625x300_01_July_23.jpg%3Fim%3DResize%3D(1230%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%20is%20upon%20us.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%2013%25%20women%20amongst%20their%20MPs.%20Their%20alliance%20partners%2C%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20(JD-U)%20and%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%2C%20have%2017%25%20and%206%25%20women%20MPs%2C%20respectively.%20The%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20has%2014%25%20women%20MPs%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20has%2013%25.%20Of%20the%2012%20candidates%20who%20were%20given%20tickets%20by%20the%20All%20India%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%2C%2011%20won.%20That's%20a%20clear%20topper%2C%20with%2038%25%20of%20women%20MPs%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20hold%2026%25%20of%20seats%20in%20national%20parliaments%20around%20the%20world.%20The%20representation%20of%20women%20in%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%20is%20half%20of%20this%20-%20a%20measly%2013.6%25.%20This%20is%20down%20from%20the%2014.4%25%20of%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Women%20comprise%20nearly%20half%20of%20India's%20electorate.%20Yet%2C%20in%20150%20constituencies%2C%20there%20was%20not%20even%20a%20single%20woman%20on%20the%20ballot!%20India%20ranks%20145%20out%20of%20185%20countries%20in%20terms%20of%20women's%20representation%20in%20the%20lower%20house%20of%20parliaments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWest%20Bengal's%20Women%20MPs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20country%2C%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20women%20candidates%20who%20won%20from%20a%20state%20in%20the%20election%20for%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%20came%20from...%20you%20guessed%20it%20right%3A%20West%20Bengal.%20You%20would%20recall%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20began%20his%20campaign%20in%20West%20Bengal%20by%20addressing%20rallies%20in%20three%20constituencies%20-%20Arambagh%2C%20Krishnanagar%20and%20Barasat%20-%20all%20three%20with%20sitting%20women%20MPs.%20To%20further%20heighten%20the%20pitch%2C%20Modi%2C%20the%20BJP's%20lead%20campaigner%2C%20spoke%20to%20the%20two%20women%20BJP%20candidates%20from%20these%20constituencies.%20In%20what%20might%20be%20a%20first%2C%20these%20private%20telephone%20calls%20were%20then%20widely%20amplified%20in%20the%20media.%20Did%20any%20of%20this%20work%3F%20No.%20The%20BJP%20lost%20all%20three%20seats.%20Trinamool's%20Mitali%20Bag%2C%20a%2047-year-old%20Integrated%20Child%20Development%20Services%20(ICDS)%20worker%2C%20won%20Arambagh.%20Barasat%20and%20Krishnanagar%20were%20convincingly%20retained%20by%20Dr%20Kakoli%20Ghosh%20Dastidar%20and%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20looking%20forward%20to%20meeting%20two%20young%20ladies%20in%20Parliament%20-%20both%20of%20them%20a%20few%20years%20younger%20than%20my%20daughter.%20Sanjana%20Jatav%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%2026-year-old%20Dalit%20woman%20who%20won%20from%20Bharatpur%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Priya%20Saroj%20of%20the%20SP%2C%20the%2025-year-old%20Dalit%20who%20won%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20In%20Gujarat%2C%20first-time%20contender%20Geniben%20Nagaji%20Thakor%20became%20the%20first%20woman%20candidate%20to%20win%20the%20Banaskantha%20seat%20in%20over%20six%20decades.%20Historic%20mandates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20their%20hot%20air%20on%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20(Act)%2C%20the%20number%20of%20female%20candidates%20fielded%20by%20the%20BJP%20who%20won%20in%202024%20came%20down%20by%2030%25.%20It's%20not%20only%20about%20giving%20women%20tickets%20for%20the%20parliamentary%20elections%3B%20it%20is%20about%20placing%20them%20in%20winnable%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2072%20Ministers%20announced%20in%20the%20newly%20formed%20cabinet%2C%20only%20seven%20are%20women.%20Of%20this%2C%20only%20two%20have%20been%20given%20key%20cabinet%20positions%20of%20the%2030%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20before%20results%20were%20announced%20for%20India's%20general%20election%20this%20year%2C%20a%20Latin%20American%20country%20scripted%20history.%20The%20two%20major%20political%20coalitions%20in%20Mexico%20-%20with%20an%20electorate%20of%2096%20million%20voters%20-%20nominated%20women%20candidates%20for%20their%20Presidential%20elections.%20Ms%20Claudia%20Scheinbaum%20defeated%20Ms%20Xochitl%20Galvez%20to%20become%20the%20country's%20first%20woman%20President.%20Mexico%20achieved%20gender%20parity%20in%20Parliament%20in%202018%2C%20with%2049%25%20women%20in%20the%20Chamber%20of%20Deputies%20and%2051%25%20in%20the%20Senate.%20Bengal%20is%20getting%20there.%20The%20rest%20of%20India%20has%20a%20good%20example%20to%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20MP%2C%20leads%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718691660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F7ko6i7hc_new-parliament-ani-new-lok-sabha-ani_625x300_01_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbengal-has-lessons-for-india-in-sending-more-women-to-parliament-5914162%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20ranks%20145%20out%20of%20185%20countries%20in%20terms%20of%20women's%20representation%20in%20the%20lower%20house%20of%20parliaments.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3