0water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20is%20there%20a%20way%20for%20these%20plants%20to%20anticipate%20these%20problems%20and%20fix%20them%20in%20advance%20to%20improve%20their%20efficiency%20and%20longevity%3F%20Suffice%20it%20to%20say%20that%20there%20are%20a%20variety%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Ftopics%2Fstartup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20startups%3C%2Fa%3E%20today%20that%20are%20developing%20technological%20solutions%20for%20wastewater%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20has%20about%2090%2C000%20installed%20wastewater%20treatment%20plants.%20But%20today%2095%25%20of%20the%20market%20is%20managed%20entirely%20manually%20by%20deploying%20operators%20in%20each%20plant.%20This%20has%20several%20drawbacks%3B%20problems%20are%20detected%20about%20three%20weeks%20late%20after%20breakdowns%20and%20operators%20lack%20the%20expertise%20to%20tackle%20problems.%20Other%20technologies%20in%20the%20market%20only%20make%20dents%20in%20part%20of%20the%20problem%3B%20they%20only%20monitor%20data%20or%20automate%20the%20key%20equipment%20like%20pumps%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20months%20of%20brainstorming%20to%20understand%20how%20they%20can%20solve%20this%20problem%20in%20a%20scalable%20manner%2C%20they%20started%20Digital%20Paani%20in%20end%202020%2C%20piloted%20an%20IoT-enabled%20software%20that%20manages%20end-to-end%20operations%20of%20a%20water%20treatment%20plant%2C%20and%20saw%20%E2%80%9Cincredible%20results%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDigital%20Paani%20is%20helping%20buildings%20and%20industries%20move%20towards%20water%20neutrality%20and%20reduce%20water%20losses%20across%20their%20campus.%20To%20do%20this%2C%20Digital%20Paani%20works%20in%20a%20stepwise%20manner%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20Maximise%20recycling%20by%20ensuring%20wastewater%20infrastructure%20is%20working%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20Helping%20indu