%20innovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20we%20log%20in%20design%20inputs%20about%20the%20infrastructure%20into%20our%20software%2C%20we%20create%20standard%20operating%20procedures%20for%20operating%20the%20plant%20in%20real-time.%20Our%20client%20can%20visualise%20the%20asset%20(wastewater%20treatment%20plant)%20and%20can%20gauge%20its%20analytics%20from%20how%20much%20wastewater%20is%20getting%20treated%20to%20the%20quality%20of%20treatment%20being%20achieved%20and%20whether%20the%20equipment%20is%20functioning%20properly%20or%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mansi%20during%20an%20episode%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DH3moOD09wNk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShark%20Tank%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20other%20words%2C%20the%20client%20has%20a%20complete%20online%20software%20before%20them%20to%20visualise%20their%20asset.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20problem%20inside%20the%20plant%2C%20our%20software%20can%20assess%20and%20interpret%20data%20using%20AI%20to%20detect%20it.%20The%20best%20part%20is%20that%20clients%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20to%20be%20on%20our%20software%20to%20manage%20these%20issues.%20Management%20actions%20are%20happening%20automatically%2C%20whether%20through%20equipment%20control%20or%20by%20telling%20operators%20directly%20what%20to%20do.%20Clients%20just%20receive%20alert%20notifications%20on%20their%20WhatsApp%20number%20to%20make%20things%20easy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20product%20innovation%2C%20Mansi%20argues%2C%20also%20allows%20them%20to%20unlock%20business%20model%20innovation.%20%E2%80%9CInstead%20of%20becoming%20an%20add-on%20cost%20for%20facilities%20like%20our%20competitors%2C%20we%20can%20de-risk%20adoption%20and%20offer%20guaranteed%20savings%20through%20two%20models%20which%20no%20one%20else%20in%20the%20market%20can%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mansi%2C%20speaking%20to%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20we%20enable%20plant%20owners%20to%20manage%20plants%20using%20their%20under-utilised%20staff%20like%20electricians%20with%20our%20system%20and%20team%E2%80%99s%20remote%20management%20rather%20than%20outsourcing%20operations%20for%20lack%20of%20expertise.%20This%20allows%20them%20to%20save%20up%20to%2066%25%20of%20operating%20costs%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20as%20Rajesh%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20take%20the%20entire%20operations%20contract%20of%20a%20facility%20and%20allow%20service%20provider%20partners%20that%20provide%20physical%20services%20like%20operators%20onsite%20to%20manage%20clusters%20of%20plants%20as%20a%20fleet%20with%20a%20small%20common%20workforce%20rather%20than%20individual%20deployments.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20does%20Digital%20Paani%20work%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDigital%20Paani%20%E2%80%9Cintegrates%20every%20aspect%20of%20wastewater%20treatment%20operations%20and%20scales%20the%20expertise%20needed%20to%20handle%20facilities%E2%80%9D%20in%20three%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20First%2C%20it%20%E2%80%98knows%E2%80%99%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20plants%20by%20determining%20how%20each%20facility%20should%20operate%20given%20its%20unique%20physical%20configuration%20and%20needs.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20this%20by%20doing%20a%20design%20assessment%20of%20each%20facility%20on%20our%20software%20as%20well%20as%20capturing%20operations%20information%20from%20each%20unit%20operation%20in%20a%20facility.%20This%20data%20spans%20a%20wide%20range%2C%20from%20using%20computer%20vision%20to%20look%20at%20biological%20process%20health%2C%20to%20looking%20at%20electrical%20data%2C%20energy%20data%2C%20pressure%2C%20vibration%2C%20flow%2C%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mansi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20Second%2C%20it%20%E2%80%98tells%E2%80%99%20the%20need%20to%20the%20relevant%20stakeholders%20by%20offering%20complete%20visibility%20through%20WhatsApp%20and%20live%20dashboards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3)%20Finally%2C%20it%20%E2%80%98solves%E2%80%99%20the%20need%20by%20executing%20the%20required%20actions%20directly%20through%20automated%20workflows%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20training%20onsite%20teams%2C%20guiding%20their%20daily%20workflow%20and%20validating%20their%20work%20or%20managing%20the%20physical%20operation%20of%20equipment%20through%20our%20in-platform%20automation%20manager.%20When%20things%20start%20going%20wrong%2C%20it%20uses%20data%20streams%20from%20onsite%20sensors%20and%20electrical%20panels%20to%20diagnose%20the%20root%20cause%20of%20the%20issue%20and%20drive%20issue%20closure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20even%20recommend%20operational%20and%20physical%20improvements.%20This%20approach%20has%20transformed%20defunct%20facilities%20while%20reducing%20their%20costs%20by%20up%20to%2066%25%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Rajesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1718112556.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Here's%20how%20you%20can%20do%20water%20treatment%20with%20Digital%20Paani%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1718112556.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1718112556-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1718112556-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1718112556-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1