%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgram-unnati-1718021372.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gram%20Unnati%20works%20with%20over%20two%20lakh%20farmers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgram-unnati-1718021372.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgram-unnati-1718021372-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgram-unnati-1718021372-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgram-unnati-1718021372-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgram-unnati-1718021372-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352573%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGram%20Unnati%20works%20with%20over%20two%20lakh%20farmers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20he%20started%20Gram%20Unnati%2C%20an%20agricultural%20value%20chain%20services%20platform%20bridging%20major%20gaps%20between%20institutional%20buyers%20and%20marginal%20farmers.%20In%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20the%20company%20has%20worked%20with%20over%20two%20lakh%20farmers%20across%20seven%20states%2C%20providing%20better%20quality%20produce%20to%20buyers%20and%20increasing%20the%20incomes%20of%20farmers.%C2%A0The%20venture%20earned%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%2050%20crore%20in%20the%20last%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGetting%20farmers%20the%20right%20value%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20one-and-a-half%20year-long%20stint%20with%20the%20soybean%20farmers%20in%20Rajasthan%20opened%20his%20eyes%20to%20their%