5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Turmeric%20Powder%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAnother%20common%20ingredient%20in%20Indian%20kitchens%2C%20pure%20turmeric%20powder%20will%20settle%20down%20slowly%20when%20dissolving%20in%20water.%20Turmeric%20powder%20often%20has%20artificial%20colouring.%20In%20that%20case%2C%20it%20will%20mix%20easily%2C%20leaving%20a%20dark%20yellow%20colour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesting%20the%20purity%20of%20your%20spices%20ensures%20the%20quality%20of%20your%20cooking%20and%20the%20health%20of%20your%20loved%20ones.%20Happy%20cooking!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718022024000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D352550%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Artificial%20colours%20in%20turmeric%20powder%2C%20papaya%20seeds%20in%20pepper%20--%20spices%20in%20our%20kitchen%20could%20be%20adulterated.%20Here's%20how%20to%20ensure%20food%20safety%20at%20home.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F352550%2Fhow-to-check-spices-purity-at-home-adulteration-indian-red-chili-powder-hing-turmeric%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98UPSC%20Interviews%20Are%20Nothing%20Like%20Mock%20Interviews%E2%80%99%3A%20IAS%20Officer%20Shares%20Preparation%20Tips%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20in%20the%20real%20interview%20will%20ask%20you%20to%20propose%20a%20glass%20of%20water.%20Many%20YouTube%20Shorts%20go%20viral%20but%20such%20irrelevant%20questions%20are%20never%20asked%20in%20real%20interviews.%20Some%20people%20and%20institutes%20are%20making%20a%20mockery%20of%20the%20system.%20But%20mock%20interviews%20are%20nowhere%20close%20to%20real%20interviews%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20IAS%20Aaditya%20Pandey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20interviewer%20panel%20comprises%20five%20experts%20in%20their%2050s%20and%2060s.%20They%20have%20a%20combined%20experience%20of%20five%20times%20our%20ages.%20Except%20for%20a%20few%20coaching%20institutes%2C%20several%20others%20make%20a%20fool%20out%20of%20aspirants%2C%20like%20asking%20them%20to%20propose%20a%20glass%20of%20water%20and%20what%20to%20do%20if%20this%20was%20their%20last%20day%20of%20life.%20Do%20not%20blindly%20rely%20on%20such%20videos.%20It%20cannot%20compete%20with%20the%20experience%20of%20the%20board%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20clearing%20Prelims%20and%20Mains%2C%20candidates%20are%20required%20to%20go%20through%20the%20final%20stage%20of%20the%20UPSC%20(Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission)%20exam%20%E2%80%94%20the%20interview%20round.%20The%20goal%20of%20the%20interview%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F281857%2Fupsc-cse-interview-topper-ias-apala-mishra-score-personality-test%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epersonality%20test%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20to%20evaluate%20their%20aptitude%2C%20ability%20to%20interact%20with%20people%2C%20and%20interest%20in%20current%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20sat%20down%20with%20Aaditya%2C%20who%20secured%20190%20marks%20in%20the%20interview%20round%2C%20to%20understand%20how%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20UPSC%20interview%2C%20and%20spare%20candidates%20from%20falling%20into%20the%20trap%20of%20mock%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-2-1718008784.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Currently%2C%20Aaditya%20is%20posted%20as%20an%20assistant%20collector%20in%20Ranchi%2C%20Jharkhand.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-2-1718008784.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-2-1718008784-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-2-1718008784-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-2-1718008784-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Aaditya-Pandey-2-1718008784-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352535%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECurrently%2C%20Aaditya%20is%20posted%20as%20an%20assistant%20collector%20in%20Ranchi%2C%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20being%20a%20mischievous%20kid%20to%20an%20IAS%20officer%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAaditya%20was%20born%20into%20a%20humble%20family%20in%20Vishunpur%20Pakri%20village%20in%20Patna%2C%20Bihar.%20Like%20most%20kids%20his%20age%2C%20he%20says%20he%20was%20quite%20impish.%20%E2%80%9COnce%2C%20one%20of%20my%20teachers%20came%20to%20our%20home%20and%20straight%20away%20went%20to%20complain%20to%20my%20%3Cem%3Ebaba%20%3C%2Fem%3E(father).%20He%20said%20if%20I%20ever%20became%20serious%20about%20my%20studies%2C%20he%20would%20shave%20his%20moustache%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20Aaditya%20went%20on%20to%20pursue%20electronics%20engineering%20from%20Lovely%20Professional%20University%2C%20Punjab%2C%20and%20later%20on%20pursued%20higher%20education%20in%20business%20administration%20from%20IIT%20Roorkee.%20After%20working%20for%20two%20years%20in%20a%20private%20bank%2C%20he%20eventually%20quit%20his%20job%20to%20prepare%20for%20UPSC%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20shaped%20his%20vision%20was%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20bureaucrat%20at%20IIT%20Roorkee.%20%E2%80%9CComing%20from%20Bihar%2C%20I%20knew%20the%20charm%20that%20comes%20with%20being%20an%20IAS