region%20is%20unique%20and%20includes%20many%20water%20channels.%20The%20sea%20has%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20the%20Sundarban%20island%2C%20and%20the%20tides%20shape%20the%20island%E2%80%99s%20physical%20features.%20Cyclone-prone%2C%20it%20receives%20heavy%20rainfall%20and%20is%20low-lying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intensity%20of%20natural%20calamities%20has%20increased%20in%20recent%20years%20due%20to%20climate%20change.%C2%A0The%20region%20faces%20a%20significant%20threat%20from%20rising%20sea%20levels%20as%20many%20islands%20have%20already%20submerged%20underwater%20or%20are%20on%20the%20verge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sundarbans%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331813%2Fkochi-murukesan-plants-lakhs-of-mangrove-along-kerala-coastline-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emangrove%20forest%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20home%20to%20the%20Royal%20Bengal%20Tiger%20along%20with%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20mangrove%20species%20like%20the%20Sundari%20(Heritiera%20fomes)%2C%20Gewa%20(Excoecaria%20agallocha)%2C%20Goran%20(Ceriops%20decandra)%2C%20Keora%20(Sonneratia%20apetala)%2C%20Dhundul%20(Xylocarpus%20granatum)%20and%20Kankra%20(Bruguiera%20gymnorhiza).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3Epalli%20%3C%2Fem%3E(villages)%20in%20the%20Sundarbans%20are%20inhabited%20mostly%20by%20the%20scheduled%20caste%20communities%20who%20were%20rehabilitated%20here%20in%201957%20from%20East%20Bengal%20(present-day%20Bangladesh).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20forefathers%20migrated%20from%20Khulna%20in%201952%20and%20after%20moving%20to%20refugee%20camps%20in%20Asansol%2C%20Serampore%20and%20Canning%2C%20we%20were%20settled%20here%20by%20the%20then%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Dr%20Bidhan%20Chandra%20Ray%20in%201957%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Biswas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEach%20family%20was%20given%20a%20land%20measuring%20nine%20%3Cem%3Ebighas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20as%20f